<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #a4c639;
    }

    table {
      width: 60%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 8px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Welcome to Chicky Cart</h2>
  <p>Dear <%= @admin_user[:new_admin].email %>,</p>
  <p>Thank you for signing up as an administrator for Chicky Cart. Please use the following credentials to log in to your admin account:</p>
  <table>
    <tr>
      <th>Email:</th>
      <td><%= @admin_user[:new_admin].email %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Password:</th>
      <td>password</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <p>We hope you have a great experience using Chicky Cart. If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
  <p>Sincerely,<br>
  The Chicky Cart Team</p>
</body>
</html>
